Author: EmpireStateBitch
Text: Exactly. If I could only have a normal approach and eat a normal amount instead of all or nothing. Sigh.

Author: algolde
Text: So true. I throw out my sandwich during lunch, eating almonds and berries, then I come home and eat rice and sweets and chocolate. As soon as I mess up (I'm *attempting* keto) I just think 'oh well'. Might as well eat every carb in existence while I still can.
